    "updated_at": "2016-01-27T23:26:19Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "AutoTarget _did_ change in this release. It will prioritizes targets based on preferred armament and then distance. i.e. Closest target that can be hit by the main weapon, if none then closest that can be hit by the secondary, etc.\n\nHowever, once it has a target it won't change unless that first target becomes invalid again (dead, out of range, etc).\n"
